Home page:  http://www.inf.puc-rio.br/~roberto/lpeg/[re.html]
Last update: lpeg-0.12.2 in 2015.03

Install:  
  Run the makefile contained in the lpeg-0.12.x folder in this directory.  
  MacOSX : make macosx [ LUADIR=/path/to/luajit/include ]
  Linux  : make linux  [ LUADIR=/path/to/luajit/include ]
  Windows: see http://lua-users.org/lists/lua-l/2007-05/msg00364.html

Cleaning:
  make clean

Usage:
  local lpeg, re = require "lib.lpeg"
